pe": "text", "text": "Added dedicated coverage test:\n\n- `tests/src/org.springframework/spring-core/5.3.15/src/test/java/org_springframework/spring_core/MixinEmitterTest.java`\n\nThe test exercises `org.springframework.cglib.proxy.Mixin.create(...)` with explicit interface delegate classes, which routes through `MixinEmitter` and reaches `Class#getMethods()` in `MixinEmitter.getMethods(...)`.\n\nIt also:\n- Keeps the test outside Spring’s package.\n- Uses public API only, without direct reflection.\n- Handles Native Image unsupported dynamic class generation via `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(...)`.\n- Avoids hardcoded artifact versions.\n\nPer instruction, I did not compile or run the tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07cf8a270e06f7410169f5afb4dcd4819c9e7606861f982d05\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 516, "output": 434, "cacheRead": 29184, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30134, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777708974251, "responseId": "resp_07cf8a270e06f7410169f5afaec0a0819cba401e320a644e85"}, "toolResults": []}
